s%3A%2F%2Fwww.ngfa.org%2F2024%2F09%2F27%2Fngfa-leads-effort-to-address-a-trifecta-of-transportation-trouble-affecting-agriculture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Grain%20and%20Feed%20Association%2C%20or%20NGFA%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20CEO%20Mike%20Seyfert%20warned%20that%20the%20strike%20could%20have%20devastating%20impact%20on%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20thing%20NFGA%20members%20or%20the%20agricultural%20community%20can%20afford%20right%20now%20is%20a%20breakdown%20in%20any%20part%20of%20our%20nation's%20shipping%20network%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2040%25%20of%20the%20US'%20agricultural%20exports%20shipped%20in%20containers%20move%20through%20the%20East%20and%20Gulf%20Coast%20ports%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Friday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ngfa.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FRail%2FAg-Letter-on-Shipping-Disruptions.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20association%20to%20the%20White%20House%20sent%20ahead%20of%20the%20industrial%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20association%20that%20represented%20200%20farm%20groups%20had%20warned%20of%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20supply%20chain%20that%20would%20%26quot%3Bquickly%20reverberate%20throughout%20the%20agricultural%20economy%2C%20shutting%20down%20operations%20and%20potentially%20lowering%20farmgate%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeyfert%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnewsletters%2Fweekly-agriculture%2F2024%2F09%2F30%2Fag-braces-for-port-strike-00181624%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolitico%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday%20that%20while%20some%20farm%20exports%20can%20be%20moved%20to%20the%20West%20Coast%20for%20shipping%2C%20there's%20probably%20not%20enough%20capacity%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20see%20increased%20shipping%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20would%20impact%20agribusinesses%20and%20producers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20agricultural%20commodities%20are%20typically%20shipped%20in%20bulk%20carriers%20rather%20than%20in%20container%20ships%2C%20so%20the%20strike%20wouldn't%20impact%20most%20wheat%2C%20maize%20and%2C%20soybeans%20exports%2C%20wrote%20Joseph%20Glauber%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20DC-based%20International%20Food%20Policy%20Research%20Institute%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifpri.org%2Fblog%2Fthe-likely-u-s-longshoreman-strike-and-its-implications-for-agricultural-trade%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMonday%20report.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20US%20meat%2C%20dairy%2C%20and%20poultry%20exports%20could%20be%20disrupted%2C%20hitting%20developing%20countries%20hard%2C%20wrote%20Glauber.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20half%2C%20or%20%247.15%20billion%20worth%2C%20of%20beef%2C%20pork%2C%20poultry%2C%20dairy%2C%20and%20egg%20exports%20to%20development%20countries%20last%20year%20were%20exported%20via%20the%20East%20and%20Gulf%20Coast%20ports%2C%20according%20to%20Glauber.%20This%20excludes%20exports%20to%20Mexico%2C%20much%20of%20which%20is%20shipped%20via%20truck%20or%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20prolonged%20strike%20would%20force%20importers%20to%20seek%20alternative%20supplies%2C%20either%20from%20West%20Coast%20ports%20or%20other%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Glauber.%20%26quot%3BUS%20meat%2C%20dairy%2C%20and%20poultry%20exports%20are%20especially%20vulnerable.%20Some%20of%20the%20costs%20of%20higher%20transport%20costs%20would%20be%20borne%20by%20importers%20(through%20higher%20prices).%20US%20producers%20would%20also%20lose%20through%20lower%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELogistics%20experts%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fport-strike-could-wreck-us-economy-with-price-increases-scarcity-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Tim%20Paradis%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20port%20strike%20could%20damage%20the%20US%20economy%20badly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F10%2F01%2Fstatement-from-president-joe-biden-on-the-negotiations-between-usmx-and-the-international-longshoremens-association%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20urged%20ports%20employers%20group%20United%20States%20Maritime%20Alliance%20to%20present%20a%20fair%20offer%20to%20the%20International%20Longshoremen's%20Association%2C%20which%20represents%20the%20striking%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExecutive%20compensation%20has%20grown%20in%20line%20with%20those%20profits%20and%20profits%20have%20been%20returned%20to%20shareholders%20at%20record%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Biden.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20fair%20that%20workers%2C%20who%20put%20themselves%20at%20risk%20during%20the%20pandemic%20to%20keep%20ports%20open%2C%20see%20a%20meaningful%20increase%20in%20their%20wages%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-port-strike-hurt-agriculture-livestorck-dairy-farmers-presidential-election-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727854146000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fcd0c35ccfc192a5527999%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-port-strike-hurt-agriculture-livestorck-dairy-farmers-presidential-election-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22About%2040%25%20of%20agricultural%20exports%20ship%20in%20containers%20move%20through%20the%20East%20and%20Gulf%20Coast%20ports%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Grain%20and%20Feed%20Association.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-port-strike-hurt-agriculture-livestorck-dairy-farmers-presidentia