3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree-part%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iron%20Dome%20is%20one%20part%20of%20Israel's%20multi-tiered%20missile%20defence%20systems%20and%20is%20designed%20to%20intercept%20short-range%20rockets%20at%20a%20distance%20of%20up%20to%2070%20kilometres%20(43%20miles).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20Iron%20Dome%20battery%20is%20made%20up%20of%20three%20main%20sections%3A%20a%20radar%20detection%20system%2C%20a%20computer%20to%20calculate%20the%20incoming%20rocket's%20trajectory%2C%20and%20a%20launcher%20that%20fires%20interceptors%20if%20the%20rocket%20is%20deemed%20likely%20to%20hit%20a%20built-up%20or%20strategic%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20sits%20alongside%20other%20missile%20defence%20systems%20like%20the%20Arrow%2C%20which%20counters%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20and%20David's%20Sling%2C%20for%20medium-range%20rocket%20or%20missile%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20much%20does%20it%20cost%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20Iron%20Dome%20interceptor%20costs%20%2440%2C000%20to%20%2450%2C000%20to%20produce%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Washington-based%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20think%20tank%20estimated%20that%20a%20complete%20system%2C%20including%20the%20radar%2C%20computer%20and%20three%20to%20four%20launchers%20--%20each%20containing%20up%20to%2020%20interceptors%20--%20costs%20around%20%24100%20million%20to%20produce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%2010%20such%20systems%20in%20operation%2C%20according%20to%20Raytheon%2C%20which%20helps%20manufacture%20the%20Iron%20Dome.%20Other%20estimates%20have%20put%20the%20figure%20slightly%20higher.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBipartisan%20US%20support%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iron%20Dome%20is%20one%20of%20the%20strategic%20pillars%20of%20the%20US-Israeli%20alliance%20that%20has%20been%20followed%20by%20successive%20Democratic%20and%20Republi