ements%20on%20how%20to%20keep%20the%20border%20peaceful%20and%20tranquil%2C%20and%20those%20agreements%20were%20violated%20by%20China%20in%202020.%20And%20some%20of%20the...because%20we%20have%20forward%20deployments%20of%20our%20militaries%2C%20there%20are%20resultant%20tensions.%20And%20until%20those%20forward%20deployments%20are%20addressed%20the%20tensions%20would%20continue.%20If%20the%20tensions%20continue%2C%20it%20casts%20a%20natural%20shadow%20over%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20relationship.%20So%20our%20relationship%20hasn't%20been%20built%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20that%20the%20India-China%20standoff%20at%20the%20border%20is%20continuing%20as%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20military%20and%20diplomatic%20discussions%20did%20not%20reap%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20noted%20that%20China%20accounts%20for%20about%2031-32%20per%20cent%20of%20global%20manufacturing%20and%20stressed%20that%20it%20has%20happened%20as%20the%20international%20community%2C%20primarily%20Western-led%2C%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades%20has%20opted%20to%20collaborate%20with%20China%20for%20mutual%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20India's%20strategic%20picture%20concerning%20China%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20trade%2C%20correct%20me%20if%20I%20am%20wrong.%20I%20think%20China%20accounts%20for%20about%2C%20globally%20about%2031-32%20per%20cent%20of%20global%20manufacturing.%20I%20think%20that%20would%20be%20the%20right%20number%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20has%20happened%20because%20over%20multiple%20decades%2C%20the%20international%20business%2C%20which%20is%20primarily%20Western-led%2C%20has%20chosen%20to%20collaborate%20with%20China%20for%20mutual%20benefit.%20So%2C%20today%2C%20for%20any%20country%2C%20if%20you%20are%20into%20any%20kind%20of%20consumption%2C%20or%20even%20into%20any%20kind%20of%20manufacturing%2C%20sourcing%20out%20of%20China%20is%20inevitable%20because%20if%20you%20are%20consuming%2C%20if%20you%20are%20not%20manufacturing%2C%20not%20consuming...you%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20the%20cheapest.%20And%20even%20if%20you%20are%20manufacturing%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20your%20components%20and%20your%20semi-processed%20materials%2C%20you%20know%2C%20come%20out%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20what%20happens%20is%20that%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20trade%20with%20China%20at%20one%20level%20is%20autonomous%20of%20the%20political%20or%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20relationship%20you%20can%20say.%20So%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20just%20a%20question%20of%20numbers.%20You%20also%20need%20to%20look%20at%20what%20is%20it%20that%20you%20are%20trading.%20Because%20there%20will%20be%20countries%2C%20that%20will%20be%20sensitive%20to%20their%20exposure.%20There%20would%20be%20countries%20that%20didn't%20care.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20for%20us%20today%2C%20because%20we%20were%20earlier%20on%20technology.%20We%20are%20very%20sensitive%20to%20our%20data%20flows.%20It's%20often%20to%20me%20a%20little%20perplexing%20that%20people%20debate%20so%20deeply%20how%20the%20data%20must%20be%20secured%20at%20home%2C%20but%20are%20less%20concerned%20about%20what%20happens%20when%20the%20data%20leaves%20your%20border.%20So%2C%20in%20a%20much%20more%20data-sensitive%20world%2C%20in%20a%20much%20more%20technology-sensitive%20world%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20important%20to%20look%20at%20what%20your%20exposures%20are%2C%20how%20you%20mitigate%20it%2C%20how%20you%20balance%20it%2C%20how%20you%20diminish%20the%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20August%2C%20India%20and%20China%20held%20the%2031st%20meeting%20of%20the%20Working%20Mechanism%20for%20Consultation%20and%20Coordination%20on%20India-China%20Border%20Affairs%20(WMCC)%20in%20Bejing%2C%20and%20the%20two%20sides%20decided%20to%20jointly%20uphold%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20border%20areas