w-shucks%20demeanor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20reason%20the%20region%20is%20known%20for%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20passive%20aggressiveness.%20And%20there%20were%20certainly%20outright%20moments%20of%20aggression%20and%20disagreement.%20In%20particular%2C%20Walz%20and%20Vance%20traded%20barbs%20over%20Trump's%20actions%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20and%20during%20the%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20Capitol%20riot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I've%20enjoyed%20tonight's%20debate%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20commonality%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Walz%20said%2C%20before%20tearing%20into%20Vance's%20defense%20of%20Trump's%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalz%20added%20that%20he%20couldn't%20believe%20that%20Vance%20would%20offer%20a%20direct%20answer%20to%20whether%20or%20not%20Trump%20had%20really%20lost%20the%202020%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20one%20is%20troubling%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Walz%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20say%20that%20because%20we%20need%20to%20tell%20the%20story.%20The%20fact%20is%20Donald%20Trump%20refused%20to%20acknowledge%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20shouldn't%20go%20unnoticed%20that%20Vance%20and%20Walz%20tore%20into%20each%20other%20in%20deeply%20personal%20ways%20ahead%20of%20the%20debate.%20Vance%20accused%20Walz%20of%20abandoning%20his%20National%20Guard%20unit%20by%20retiring%20before%20his%20service%20members%20were%20deployed%20to%20Iraq.%20Walz%20became%20the%20Democratic%20vice%20presidential%20nominee%20in%20large%20part%20because%20he%20called%20Vance%20and%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bweird.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227fc5d462-af46-4a49-8dce-12a2b4db5ff7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeither%20side%20truly%20seized%20what%20may%20be%20the%20last%20big%20moment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJournalists%20and%20pundits%20often%20joke%20about%20how%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvance-walz-vice-presidential-debate-preview-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%