2Ftim-walz-jd-vance-shake-hands-before-us-vice-presidential-debate-starts-6696928%5C%22%3Eshowdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Walz%2C%20the%20Democratic%20Minnesota%20governor%20chosen%20by%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20and%20Vance%2C%20the%20Republican%20senator%20from%20Ohio%20who%20is%20Donald%20Trump's%20running%20mate%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20last%20of%20the%202024%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20refused%20a%20second%20debate%20with%20Vice%20President%20Harris%2C%20meaning%20this%20could%20be%20the%20final%20chance%20to%20see%20the%20two%20tickets%20go%20head%20to%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20question%20of%20the%20night%20was%20on%20Iran's%20missile%20attack%20on%20Israel%20and%20Walz%20immediately%20turned%20his%20fire%20on%20Trump's%20foreign%20policy%20record%2C%20slamming%20the%20ex-president%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Bturn%20towards%26quot%3B%20Russia's%20Vladimir%20Putin%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20United%20States%20from%20the%202015%20Iran%20nuclear%20disarmament%20deal%2C%20known%20as%20the%20JCPOA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20much%20as%20Governor%20Walz%20just%20accused%20Donald%20Trump%20of%20being%20an%20agent%20of%20chaos%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20actually%20delivered%20stability%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20countered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20he%20did%20it%20by%20establishing%20effective%20deterrence.%20People%20were%20afraid%20of%20stepping%20out%20of%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance%2C%2040%2C%20and%20Walz%2C%2060%2C%20each%20claim%20to%20be%20the%20true%20voice%20of%20the%20crucial%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-the-vance-walz-debate-boils-down-to-contrasting-versions-of-masculinity-6683266%5C%22%3Eswing%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20--%20including%20Michigan%20and%20Wisconsin%20--%20that%20could%20decide%20an%20election%20that%20remains%20on%20a%20knife%20edge%20with%20five%20weeks%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20suggests%20vice-presidential%20debates%20rarely%20move%20the%20dial%20much.%20But%20in%20an%20election%20campaign%20that%20has%20seen%20Harris%20step%20in%20for%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20unprecedentedly%20late%20in%20the%20game%2C%20Tuesday's%20contest%20may%20have%20added%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20offered%20words%20of%20encouragement%20for%20Walz%2C%20telling%20him%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20ahead%20of%20his%20big%20night%3A%20%26quot%3BCoach%2C%20I%20got%20your%20back%20tonight!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20race%20has%20seen%20Vance%20and%20Trump%20use%20increasingly%20divisive%20rhetoric%20and%20even%20falsely%20accuse%20immigrants%20of%20eating%20people's%20pets%20--%20meaning%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-vance-walz-us-vice-presidential-debate-all-you-need-to-know-6672924%5C%22%3Edebate%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20make%20for%20fiery%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20whet%20a%20lot%20of%20people's%20appetites%20for%20November%205%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20Whalen%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20social%20sciences%20at%20Boston%20University%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20debate%20itself%20risked%20being%20overshadowed%20by%20Mideast%20tensions%2C%20after%20Iran%20launched%20ballistic%20missiles%20against%20Israel%2C%20which%20said%20it%20largely%20repelled%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20visiting%20swing%20state%20Wisconsin%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20focused%20on%20the%20crisis%2C%20insisting%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20I%20were%20in%20charge%2C%20today's%20attack%20on%20Israel%20never%20would%20have%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20Harris%20and%20Walz%20win%2C%20he%20warned%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world%20goes%20up%20in%20smoke.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20Vance%20to%20%26quot%3Bhave%20fun%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20what%20advice%20he%20would%20give%2C%20praising%20his%20running%20mate%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bwarrior.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20for%20her%20part%20pledged%20her%20%26quot%3Bunwavering%26quot%3B%20commitment%20to%20the%20security%20of%20Israel%20after%20Iran%20launched%20what%20she%20called%20%26quot%3Ba%20reckless%20and%20brazen%20attack%26quot%3B%20on%20America's%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBS%20clash%20comes%20as%20several%20states%20dig%20out%20from%20enormous%20storm%20Helene%2C%20which%20has%20left%20at%20least%20150%20people%20dead%20and%20brought%20misery%20to%20many%20thousands%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'High%20drama'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalz%20and%20Vance%20were%20each%20picked%20by%20their%20bosses%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20voters%20in%20the%20Midwestern%20battlegrounds%20where%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20country's%20idiosyncratic%20electoral%20college%20system%2C%20a%20few%20thousand%20votes%20could%20determine%20who%20wins%20the%20White%20House%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20are%20military%20veterans%20with%20strong%20blue-collar%20credentials.%20Vance%20authored%20the%20Rust%20Belt%20memoir%20%26quot%3BHillbilly%20Elegy%26quot%3B%20while%20Walz%20boasts%20a%20folksy%20persona%20as%20a%20former%20teacher%20and%20football%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20similarities%20end%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20combative%20Vance%20shares%20Trump's%20penchant%20for%20courting%20controversy%2C%20whether%20by%20smearing%20Democrats%20as%20%26quot%3Bchildless%20cat%20ladies%26quot%3B%20or%20by%20boosting%20false%20claims%20that%20Haitians%20living%20in%20an%20Ohio%20town%20ate%20residents'%20pets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20goal%20will%20be%20to%20overcome%20polls%20that%20initially%20had%20him%20as%20one%20of%20the%20least%20popular%20VP%20nominees%20in%20history%20after%20a%20series%20of%20previous%20comments%20on%20women%20and%20abortion%20were%20unearthed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVance%20has%20to%20be%20careful%20because%20I%20think%20a%20trap%20has%20been%20laid%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Whalen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cheery%20Walz%20will%20be%20seeking%20to%20introduce%20himself%20to%20a%20public%20that%20barely%20knows%20him%2C%20after%20Harris's%20swift%20rise%20to%20replace%20Biden%20as%20the%20Democratic%20nominee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20became%20a%20hit%20with%20Democrats%20for%20branding%20Vance%20and%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bweird%26quot%3B%20and%20for%20his%20progressive%20politics%20--%20but%20that%20will%20be%20a%20target%20for%20Vance%20as%20he%20and%20Trump%20seek%20to%20paint%20Walz%20and%20Harris%20as%20%26quot%3BMarxists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance%20%26quot%3Bis%20going%20up%20against%20a%20moron%2C%20a%20total%20moron%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20Monday%20on%20Fox%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727838840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fg74lo93o_tim-walz-jd-vance-veep-debate-us_625x300_02_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-elections-2024-us-veep-candidates-take-on-middle-east-crisis-in-pre-election-debate-6696960%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20vice%20presidential%20contenders%20JD%20Vance%20and%20Tim%20Walz%20took%20on%20the%20crisis%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20as%20they%20met%20Tuesday%20for%20what%20could%20be%20an%20unusually%20important%20undercard%20debate%2C%20competing%20for%20decisive%20votes%20weeks%20before%20the%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-elections-2024-us-veep-candidates-take-on-middle-east-crisis-in-pre-election-debate-6696960%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Padyatris%20go%20on%20hunger%20strike%20after%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%2C%20173%20others%20detained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%2