essinsider.com%2Fsigns-youre-in-a-healthy-relationship-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggling%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-if-you-hate-job-cant-quit-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunsatisfied%20with%20my%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20constantly%20felt%20anxious%20and%20on%20edge.%20At%20a%20friend's%20wedding%2C%20where%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20be%20a%20bridesmaid%2C%20my%20social%20anxiety%20was%20so%20intense%20that%20I%20had%20one%20too%20many%20glasses%20of%20wine%20and%20sat%20out%20most%20of%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae5393c5-d981-4234-b770-ec2508d2d7d1%5C%22%3EI%20felt%20lonely%20after%20moving%20to%20Spain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20led%20to%20an%20uptick%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmodern-loneliness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloneliness%20around%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20lockdowns%20and%20travel%20restrictions%20kept%20people%20away%20from%20family%20and%20friends.%20And%20I%20was%20no%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202020%2C%20I'd%20just%20spent%20my%20first%20year%20and%20a%20half%20in%20Seville%2C%20Spain.%20Plans%20to%20integrate%2C%20learn%20Spanish%2C%20and%20meet%20new%20people%20were%20interrupted%20by%20lockdowns%20and%20panic%20over%20new%20virus%20variants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20had%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-spain-for-sun-fun-affordable-better-life-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20moved%20to%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E%20thinking%20we'd%20travel%20around%20and%20enjoy%20a%20great%20quality%20of%20life%20while%20working%20remotely.%20Instead%2C%20with%20travel%20bookings%20canceled%20and%20meetups%20kiboshed%2C%20I%20settled%20into%20a%20rigorous%20work-from-home%20routine%2C%20interspersed%20with%20immigration%20paperwork%20and%20reading%20up%20on%20vaccines.%