you're%20light%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%2C%20another%20member%20from%20the%20UK%2C%20moved%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-places-to-visit-in-fall-no-crowds-frequent-traveler-2024-9%23you-can-bypass-fall-altogether-in-south-island-new-zealand-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESeville%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20northern%20Spain%20after%20his%20marriage%20also%20broke%20down.%20When%20he%20attended%20his%20first%20improv%20session%2C%20he%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20expect%2C%20but%20he%20says%20he's%20so%20happy%20to%20have%20stepped%20outside%20his%20comfort%20zone.%20%26quot%3BDoing%20improv%20has%20led%20me%20to%20meet%20so%20many%20like%20minded%20people%20whom%20I've%20had%20such%20a%20good%20time%20with.%20I%20haven't%20laughed%20so%20much%20in%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20realized%20that%20improv%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20times%20I%20can%20let%20my%20inner%20child%20run%20free.%20Deep%20connections%20have%20formed%2C%20and%20I%20now%20feel%20empowered%20to%20let%20go%20and%20allow%20myself%20to%20be%20authentic%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20front%20of%20a%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20personal%20essay%20to%20share%20about%20challenges%20faced%20while%20living%20abroad%3F%20Get%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20editor%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aakarplus%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eakarplus%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-millennial-living-abroad-spain-overcome-loneliness-friends-improv-comedy-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727828042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f27eccd17aa3c7b2b55212%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi