eone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20saving%20someone%20from%20drowning%20in%20a%20swimming%20pool%2C%20you%20are%20working%20in%20a%20confined%20space%20with%20four%20corners%20no%20matter%20its%20size.%20You%20know%20exactly%20where%20to%20jump%20in%2C%20save%20the%20person%20and%20drop%20them%20off%20at%20any%20given%20edge%20of%20the%20pool.%20In%20the%20sea%2C%20you%20can%20only%20save%20someone%20by%20taking%20them%20back%20one%20way.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20confined%20space.%20Another%20thing%20I%20learnt%20about%20were%20rip%20currents%20%E2%80%94%20strong%20and%20narrow%20currents%20that%20can%20pull%20you%20into%20the%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Drishti%20Marine%20is%20the%20designated%20first%20responder%20for%20any%20beach-related%20emergency%2C%20including%20cases%20of%20marine%20strandings.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20Rajiv%20claims%20that%20its%20450-plus%20strong%20force%20of%20%E2%80%98lifesavers%E2%80%99%20(lifeguards)%20has%20saved%20about%207%2C700%20people%20from%20drowning%20off%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20coastline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPatrolling%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20shores%20and%20saving%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeaches%20in%20Goa%20are%20divided%20into%20zones%3A%20swim%20areas%20marked%20by%20red%20and%20yellow%20flags%2C%20no-swim%20zones%20by%20red%20flags%2C%20and%20watersport%20areas%20by%20black-and-white%20flags.%20High-footfall%20beaches%20have%20dedicated%20lifesaver%20towers%20offering%20a%20clear%20vantage%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rajiv%20elaborates%2C%20%E2%80%9CSwim%20zones%20are%20continuously%20monitored%20by%20lifesavers%20equipped%20with%20binoculars%2C%20jet%20skis%2C%20spine%20boards%2C%20surfboards%2C%20and%20rescue%20tubes.%20When%20a%20person%20in%20distress%20is%20spotted%20off%20the%20beach%2C%20the%20on-duty%20lifesaver%20notifies%20other%20lifesavers%20via%20radio.%20The%20rescue%20team%20rushes%20to%20assist%20the%20person%20in%20distress%2C%20alerts%20backup%20to%20call%20an%20ambulance%2C%20and%20accompanies%20the%20rescued%20individual%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20evaluation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lifeguards%20along%20the%20Goan%20shoreline%2C%20prepared%20to%20save%20lives.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Equipment-1727448812-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367904%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELifeguards%20along%20the%20Goan%20shoreline%2C%20prepared%20to%20save%20lives.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLifesaver%20towers%20are%20stocked%20with%20emergency%20medical%20equipment%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20first%20aid%20kits%2C%20spine%20boards%2C%20surfboards%2C%20rescue%20boards%2C%20rescue%20tubes%2C%20handheld%20radio%20sets%2C%20bag%20valve%20masks%20to%20assist%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F206387%2Fcpr-first-aid-basic-life-support-cardiopulmonary-resuscitation-mouth-to-mouth-health-care-medical-emergency%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECardiopulmonary%20Resuscitation%20(CPR)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Automated%20External%20Defibrillator%20(A.E.D.)%20machines.%20The%20official%20beach%20jeeps%20are%20on%20standby%20to%20transport%20patients%20or%20distressed%20individuals%20to%20nearby%20health%20facilities%20or%20ambulances.%20Lifesavers%20are%20also%20trained%20in%20first%20aid%20to%20provide%20immediate%20assistance%20during%20medical%20emergencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWorking%20in%20Calangute%20beach%2C%20I%20do%20approximately%2030%20rescues%20a%20month%20because%20there%20is%20always%20a%20large%20crowd%20present%20there.%20Rescues%20usually%20happen%20between%20an%20approximate%20range%20of%2030%20to%2050%20metres%20into%20the%20sea%20%5Bfrom%20the%20shoreline%5D.%20Away%20from%20the%20shoreline%20at%20Calangute%20Beach%2C%20we%20encounter%20a%20lot%20of%20rip%20currents.%20When%20a%20tourist%20encounters%20a%20rip%20current%20by%20swimming%20too%20far%20from%20the%20shore%2C%20they%20panic%20because%20the%20water%20is%20pulling%20them%20into%20the%20sea%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20are%20the%20heroes%20behind%20the%20rescues%20chosen%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMen%20and%20women%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2030%20years%20who%20know%20swimming%20and%20are%20committed%20to%20saving%20victims%20are%20eligible%20to%20become%20Drishti%20lifesavers%2C%20notes%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COur%20hiring%20checklist%20includes%20thorough%20physical%20tests%2C%20interviews%2C%20reference%20checks%2C%20and%20police%20verification.%20The%20physically%20demanding%20nature%20of%20a%20lifesaver%20requires%20that%20men%20and%20wo