-fed%20rivers%20like%20the%20Teesta%20and%20Ganga.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20particular%20stream%20has%20become%20perennial%2C%20Snehal%20informs%20me%2C%20explaining%20that%20the%20abundant%20groundwater%20provides%20a%20constant%20flow.%20Members%20of%20the%20Tieedi%20team%20have%20also%20placed%20nets%20along%20the%20stream%E2%80%99s%20borders%20to%20prevent%20people%20from%20dumping%20garbage.%20An%20interesting%20technique%20they%20employ%20is%20setting%20up%20a%20small%20temple%20at%20a%20part%20of%20the%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTreating%20it%20as%20an%20auspicious%20site%20prevents%20locals%20from%20dumping%20garbage%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Snehal%20explains.%20A%20tiny%20bamboo%20bridge%20connects%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20complex%2C%20and%20the%20river%E2%80%99s%20constant%20flow%20adds%20melody%20to%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20many%20birds%20inhabiting%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201545px)%20100vw%2C%201545px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221545%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bamboo%20bridge%20over%20the%20perennial%20stream%20leading%20to%20an%20eco-hut%20in%20Tieedi.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382.jpeg%201545w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup