ct%20of%20the%20loss%20is%20finally%20evident.%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20pangolins%2C%20our%20crops%20are%20dying%2C%E2%80%9D%20exclaims%20Thomas%2C%20the%20Church%20catechist%20of%20Razai%20Khullen%20village.%20Pangolins%20and%20crops%20%E2%80%94%20what%20could%20be%20the%20connection%3F%20%E2%80%9COur%20houses%20are%20falling%20and%20our%20forests%20are%20decaying%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20fuelling%20my%20curiosity%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20week%2C%20I%20travel%20with%20a%20team%20of%20conservationists%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360895%2Fvivek-menon-wildlife-trust-of-india-wildlife-conservation-anti-poaching-elephant-corridors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20(WTI)%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20understand%20the%20implications%20and%20what%20is%20being%20done%20to%20ensure%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20pangolins%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJoining%20tribes%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20pangolins%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20in%20Chingjaro%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20last%20villages%20in%20the%20Indian%20state%20of%20Manipur%20%E2%80%94%20just%20a%20few%20kilometres%20from%20the%20borders%20of%20Myanmar.%20In%20between%2C%20are%20lush%20mountains%20connected%20by%20a%20narrow%2C%20remote%20and%20dodgy%20road.%20Long%20before%20reaching%20the%20border%2C%20you%20can%20already%20feel%20a%20distinct%20change%20in%20the%20surroundings.%20This%20place%20is%20nothing%20like%20Imphal%2C%20the%20state%20capital%20where%20I%20started%20my%20journey%20a%20few%20days%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20been%20making%20headlines%20in%20recent%20years%20due%20to%20community%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%2C%20Naga%20and%20Kuki%20tribes%20of%20the%20state.%20Hundreds%20of%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20several%20homes%20have%20been%20burnt%20and%20thousa